 <body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
  Ciao,<br /> We would like to do a video call with you to understand your requests.<br /> When are you available to chat?<br /> Here the link to book the call!<br /> <a href="https://calendly.com/fabiodexsrl">https://calendar.app.google/etjBqL5VFZSZH4b89</a><br /> After the video call, you will receive a proposal made especially for your event, with each service separate so you can decide at the end what you plan to keep.<br /> We still have availability for that date. In order to establish a budget, we need more details, such as:&nbsp;<br /> • Hours of all the wedding day<br /> • Location<br /> • No. Days of party&nbsp;<br /> • No. Guests&nbsp;<br /> • No. environments where the music (eg area aperitifs/ /Dinner and dance), and especially to know if they are different areas.<br /> • know if there will be a ceremony on site&nbsp;<br /> • know if you have a wedding planner<br /> • know if there are other artists or if you are looking for these<br /> • know if there will be other productions audio / lighting or if you are looking for this<br /> • which theme have you chosen&nbsp;<br /> • which vendors have you chosen until now and who they are<br /> • from which country you came from and where you find our contact<br /> <br /> <a href="https://fabiodex2023--devalfano.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/7a0000005D2e/a/7a000000RYig/Lf9lmTx3ggE.Q4DS.Yu5oHy7Dr5zgWTuOPU9LKm.gFw"><img alt="Copertina_Price_List" src="{[devName:Copertina_Price_List]}" style="max-width: 697.3px" title="Copertina_Price_List" /></a><br /> <br /> <br /> Here you can find our illustrated catalog for fabiodex’s sound design production.<br /> &nbsp;
